### Create a book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "author": "Robert C. Martin",
  "isbn": "9780132350884",
  "category": "Software Engineering",
  "totalCopies": 3
}

### List books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books

### Search available books
GET http://localhost:8080/api/books?keyword=clean&available=true

### Create a member
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Asha Sharma",
  "email": "asha@example.com",
  "phone": "+91-9876543210"
}

### Borrow a book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/loans/borrow
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 1,
  "memberId": 1,
  "loanDays": 14
}

### Return a book
POST http://localhost:8080/api/loans/1/return

### List overdue loans
GET http://localhost:8080/api/loans?overdue=true
